"title": "8619: prayer, in the church",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8619",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The prayer life of the NT provides a pattern from which the modern church can learn, both in terms of the importance of prayer, and also matters for prayer.</p>\n<h2>Prayer was at the centre of the life of the early church</h2>\n<h3>They prayed when they met together</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:14\">ACT 1:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:42\">ACT 2:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:23-Acts4:31\">ACT 4:23–4:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:12\">ACT 12:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:36\">ACT 20:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:5\">ACT 21:5</a></p>\n<h3>They prayed about the selection and ordination of Christian leaders</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:2-Acts13:3\">ACT 13:2–13:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:24-Acts1:25\">ACT 1:24–1:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:6\">ACT 6:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:23\">ACT 14:23</a></p>\n<h3>They prayed during persecution</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:5\">ACT 12:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:59-Acts7:60\">ACT 7:59–7:60</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:12\">ACT 12:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:22-Acts16:25\">ACT 16:22–16:25</a></p>\n<h3>They prayed for healing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:40\">ACT 9:40</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:7-Acts28:8\">ACT 28:7–28:8</a></p>\n<h2>The apostles' teaching on prayer in church life</h2>\n<h3>The importance of prayer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:2\">COL 4:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:12\">ROM 12:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:18\">EPH 6:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:17\">1TH 5:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:1\">1TI 2:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:7\">1PE 4:7</a></p>\n<h3>Prayer for the spread of the gospel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:3-Col4:4\">COL 4:3–4:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:19-Eph6:20\">EPH 6:19–6:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:1\">2TH 3:1</a></p>\n<h3>Prayer for the sick</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:14\">JAS 5:14</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Prayer for sinners</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:16-1John5:17\">1JN 5:16–5:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:16\">JAS 5:16</a></p>\n<h3>Prayer for God's servants</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:30\">ROM 15:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:11\">2CO 1:11</a></p>\n<h3>Orderly conduct of public prayer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:4-1Cor11:5\">1CO 11:4–11:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:13-1Cor11:15\">1CO 11:13–11:15</a></p>\n<h2>The practice of the apostles</h2>\n<h3>Prayer was central to their ministry</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:3-Acts6:4\">ACT 6:3–6:4</a></strong></p>\n<h3>They prayed for the church</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:9-Col1:10\">COL 1:9–1:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:16-Eph1:21\">EPH 1:16–1:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:16-Eph3:19\">EPH 3:16–3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:9-Phil1:11\">PHP 1:9–1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:3\">COL 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:2\">1TH 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:11-2Thess1:12\">2TH 1:11–1:12</a></p>",
